                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">论述太琐碎，而且缺少结论。从没读过一本书，译者边译边标注出作者的这么多（考据and/or理解上的）错误的。第一印象四星，为译者加一星，为作者减两星。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="912845367">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-912845367" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-912845367" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="912845367">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/30364990/">张天戈</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2015-04-14</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">作者真的找了不少资料 但是硬往地域特殊性上靠 感觉很难让人信服 所以看这本书的时候完全不用搭理作者的废话 只要看资料就行了 </p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="843045794">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-843045794" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-843045794" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="843045794">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/isleofzoe/">乌鸫</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2015-11-21</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">细节杂芜，脉络不清</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="831445055">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-831445055" class="vote-count">3</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-831445055" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="831445055">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3366974/">[已注销]</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2014-07-31</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">书名和副标题都有点言过其实，作者书里论述的具体内容并没有那么血腥暴力。当然，作为对地方志进行的一种当代处理，本书的写作策略还是值得一提的（虽然并不好过沈艾娣的《梦醒子》）</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

